title: Hypnosis Network - The Headache Solution
description:
Hypnosis: The Headache Solution
By Maggie Philips, Ph.D., director of the California Institute of Clinical Hypnosis

1 CD program by the Hypnosis Network.
Excellent for individuals with no prior exposure to hypnosis.
 
Created by Maggie Phillips, this hypnosis program will help you reverse the pain associated with headaches. Designed for situations where typical interventions are not enough, this program will help you stop the chain reaction that causes severe headache pain. By learning how to relax in the face of triggers which normally cause headaches, you will expercience a new sense of control and comfort.

Learn how to:

-Transform your headache pain
-Experience lasting relief
-Relax before you headache begins
-Reverse or block headache pain
-Change your pain pathways
-Create new responses to headache triggers

Tracks:
-Using Hypnosis with Headaches        (7:39)
-The Basic Headache Prescription      (1:56)
-Relax Away the Headache              (18:14)
-Headache Triggers                    (2:14)
-Creating a New Response to Triggers  (19:40)

Tracks 3 and 5 are the actual hypnosis sessions.

Encoded in 128 kbps AAC.
Total length: 49:41
